An automated pool cover is a valuable addition to your swimming pool and will keep it clean and clear. Designer Pool Covers offers a variety of luxurious automated covers that can retract and conceal into a stylish compartment that matches your preferred aesthetic. Get your Designer Pool Cover in Cape Town, Johannesburg, or Durban. These covers can be customised to fit swimming pools of various shapes and sizes, and Designer Pool Covers provides a selection of installation options to cater to your needs. Pool owners know the hassle of trying to protect their pool from leaves or algae – but with an automatic cover from Designer Pool Covers, you no longer need to struggle. Their covers simply slide in and out of place at the press of a button, providing a hassle-free way to keep your pool clean and warm while ensuring a safe experience for the whole family. The superior finish will blend into the aesthetic of your home and pool area when closed, too, and when not in use your rolled-up cover is neatly hidden away either above or below ground – depending on your installation. Designer Pool Covers offers a variety of custom-made, automated covers for indoor, outdoor, residential, and commercial settings. Its two main types of automated covers are the PoolDeck slatted covers and the PoolLock hydraulic vinyl covers. PoolDeck slatted covers offer elegance and style in an easy-to-operate system that works at the press of a button. Its PVC slats float on the water’s surface and the installation can be above or below ground. The above-ground option can be disguised as a bench at the edge of your pool, while the below-ground option does not interfere with your pool’s aesthetics. The PoolLock hydraulic vinyl covers are the best safety cover option on the market, as they can handle a lot of weight, the electric motor can be distanced from the pool, and they can close in less than 60 seconds. They are also durable and can be fitted to both small and large pools. Designer Pool Covers is an industry leader in the supply and installation of pool covers. It offers the finest, safest, and easiest-to-use pool covers on the market, with the most exclusive range of products that comply with international standards and trends. These covers not only provide safety and aesthetic benefits – they also keep your swimming pool clean, reduce water maintenance, and eliminate evaporation. Alongside its automated covers, Designer Pool Covers offers various manual covers – including thermal blankets to keep your pool warm – and pet and child safety covers. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-607528" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/BusTech4.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="340" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/BusTech4.jpg 640w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/BusTech4-300x159.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> Get your Designer Pool Cover in Cape Town, Johannesburg, or Durban.